sonicwave.views.about(request)[source]

This view renders the about page of the website. It displays information about the band including its history, members and influences.

sonicwave.views.albums(request)[source]

This view renders the albums page of the website. It displays a list of the band’s albums with a link to the information page of each album

sonicwave.views.home(request)[source]

This view renders the home page of the website. It requires the user to be logged in and displays a navigation bar with links to the band’s about page and album page. The home page also displays a Sonicwave logo and a background image of a sound wave. The background image is a linear gradient
